WEBVTT

00:01.200 --> 00:03.191
[ BELLS TOLLING ]

00:17.250 --> 00:24.986
Isaac:
I, ISAAC WALTON...

00:25.020 --> 00:31.129
HAVE GAZED UPON THE NAKEDNESS
OF ABIGAIL COOK...

00:33.030 --> 00:35.658
[Voice breaking ]
...AND DID KISS HER.

00:35.700 --> 00:36.223
George: AND?

00:36.270 --> 00:38.158
Isaac: AND --

00:38.200 --> 00:40.668
George: AND DID COMMIT THE SIN
OF SELF-POLLUTION.

00:40.700 --> 00:43.999
Isaac: AND COMMITI'ED
THE SIN OF SELF-POLLUTION.

00:44.040 --> 00:45.598
George:
10 HARD ONES.

00:47.210 --> 00:48.507
Isaac: [ SCREAMS ]

00:48.540 --> 00:49.541
[ LEATHER CRACKS ]

00:49.580 --> 00:51.775
[ SCREAMING ]

00:54.880 --> 00:57.189
George:
ON THIS GLORIOUS DAY,

00:57.220 --> 01:02.522
OUR BRAVE BOYS MUSTER TO FACE
THE DEVIL'S SHOCK TROOPS...

01:02.560 --> 01:05.188
FRENCH AND INDIAN SAVAGES

01:05.230 --> 01:08.722
MASSING IN THE WOODS
RIGHT OUTSIDE OUR DOORS.

01:08.760 --> 01:10.125
Isaac: [ GROANING ]

01:10.170 --> 01:11.797
George: AND WHAT ARE YOU
GOING OFF TO DEFEND?

01:11.830 --> 01:14.936
NOT SODOM, BUT SALEM.

01:14.970 --> 01:17.939
WE CANNOT EXPECT GOD
TO BE ON OUR SIDE

01:17.970 --> 01:23.602
IF WE TOLERATE ABOMINATIONS
OR THOSE WHO COMMIT THEM.

01:23.650 --> 01:26.118
YOU TWO WILL REMAIN
IN THE STOCKS OVERNIGHT.

01:26.150 --> 01:29.119
AND YOU, BOY,
WILL BEAR THE MARK OF YOUR SINS

01:29.150 --> 01:30.583
THE REST OF YOUR LIFE.

01:30.620 --> 01:32.087
Isaac: [ GROANING ]

01:32.120 --> 01:33.553
Man: HAVE MERCY!

01:33.590 --> 01:35.285
[ SIZZLING ]

01:35.320 --> 01:36.878
NO, PLEASE. PLEASE!

01:36.930 --> 01:39.797
Mr. Hale:
FOR GOD'S SAKES, SIBLEY.

01:39.830 --> 01:44.096
THE STOCKS AND THE LASHINGS
ARE PUNISHMENT ENOUGH.

01:44.130 --> 01:45.222
Isaac:
[ Sobbing ] NO!

01:45.270 --> 01:46.498
George: FORNICATOR!

01:46.540 --> 01:47.791
Isaac: [ SCREAMS ]

01:47.840 --> 01:49.569
[ CROWD GASPS ]

01:49.610 --> 01:51.635
[ SCREAMING ]

01:51.670 --> 01:54.070
John: JUDGE NOT...

01:54.110 --> 01:55.907
LEST YE BE JUDGED.

01:55.940 --> 01:57.976
George:
WHO SAID THAT?

01:58.010 --> 02:01.946
John: JESUS.
YOU MIGHT HAVE HEARD OF HIM.

02:01.980 --> 02:04.983
George: JOHN ALDEN.
[ SCOFFS ]

02:05.020 --> 02:08.979
MY RESPECT
FOR YOUR FATHER'S MEMORY

02:09.020 --> 02:11.227
CAN ONLY SHIELD YOU SO LONG.

02:12.700 --> 02:15.157
Giles: IT'S A GOOD THING
YOU'RE MUSTERING OUT TONIGHT.

02:15.200 --> 02:18.419
LIKE IT OR NOT,
SIBLEY'S IN CHARGE.

02:18.470 --> 02:19.664
HE TOLERATED YOUR FATHER,

02:19.700 --> 02:20.860
BUT HE WON'T BE HAPPY

02:20.900 --> 02:23.733
TILL HE SEES YOU SWING.

02:34.050 --> 02:36.041
[ DOG BARKING IN DISTANCE ]

02:40.660 --> 02:43.322
[ HORSE NEIGHS ]

03:02.580 --> 03:04.207
-John: HEY!
-Mary: OH!

03:04.250 --> 03:05.501
John: [ CHUCKLES ]

03:05.550 --> 03:07.074
Mary:
DIDN'T YOU LEARN ANYTHING TODAY?

03:07.120 --> 03:09.418
John: YES, YES, IF I HAVE
TO SPEND ONE MORE NIGHT

03:09.450 --> 03:11.748
UNDER THE SAME STARS
AS THAT BASTARD GEORGE SIBLEY,

03:11.790 --> 03:13.553
I WILL GUT HIM
LIKE THE PIG THAT HE IS.

03:13.590 --> 03:16.081
Mary: IF -- TALKING LIKE THAT
WILL LAND YOU IN THE STOCKS.

03:16.120 --> 03:18.259
John: NO DAY SOON.
[ SIGHS ]

03:18.290 --> 03:20.258
I'D RATHER DIE FIGHTING
THE FRENCH AND THE INDIANS

03:20.300 --> 03:23.098
THAN GET PISSED ON
BY THE GOOD SOULS OF SALEM.

03:23.130 --> 03:25.394
Mary:
SO, YOU'RE REALLY LEAVING.

03:27.140 --> 03:30.109
John: MARY, TRUST ME.

03:30.140 --> 03:32.608
I WILL COME BACK FOR YOU.

03:32.640 --> 03:34.835
HEY.

03:34.880 --> 03:37.098
LOOK.

03:37.150 --> 03:40.369
THIS IS ALL THAT I HAVE.

03:40.420 --> 03:45.039
AND I SWEAR
ON MY PARENTS' GRAVE.

03:45.090 --> 03:49.254
THIS IS MY VOW.

03:49.290 --> 03:52.919
THIS WAR WILL NOT LAST A YEAR.

04:03.440 --> 04:06.068
Man: FORWARD!

04:06.110 --> 04:08.578
STAY IN FORMATION, GENTLEMEN.

04:18.490 --> 04:20.811
[ HORSE NEIGHS ]

04:27.430 --> 04:29.421
[ BIRD CAWS ]

04:31.970 --> 04:33.267
Man: ISN'T BUT
A HALF-DAY'S RIDE.

04:33.300 --> 04:34.437
Mary:
I CAN'T MAKE IT.

04:34.470 --> 04:35.767
I THINK I'M GONNA BE SICK AGAIN.

04:35.800 --> 04:37.336
Tituba: SHH.

04:37.370 --> 04:39.008
AS SOON AS YOU SIT DOWN INSIDE,
IT WILL SE'I'I'LE.

04:39.040 --> 04:41.179
Man:
WAIT YOUR BE'I'I'ERS, GIRL.

04:41.210 --> 04:43.508
PEACE BE UPON YOU.

04:43.550 --> 04:45.040
George: AND UPON YOU.

04:46.620 --> 04:49.418
Mary:
PEACE BE UPON YOU.

04:49.450 --> 04:51.315
George: AND UPON YOU.

04:51.350 --> 04:54.285
THOUGH THERE ARE THINGS
TO BE SAID FOR WAR.

04:54.320 --> 04:57.483
GIVES A CERTAIN KIND OF MAN
SOMEPLACE TO END UP

04:57.530 --> 04:59.657
OTHER THAN
THE END OF A BRAND...

04:59.700 --> 05:02.260
OR A ROPE.

05:02.300 --> 05:04.723
YOU'LL THANK ME ONE DAY.

05:08.070 --> 05:10.038
Titu ba: STAY STRONG.

05:10.070 --> 05:12.971
AFI'ER TONIGHT,
IT WILL ALL BE OVER.

05:13.010 --> 05:14.375
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

05:31.590 --> 05:33.729
Mary:
[ BREATHING HEAVILY]

05:33.760 --> 05:36.058
TITU BA, WAIT.

05:36.100 --> 05:37.829
I'VE CHANGED MY MIND.
I WANT TO GO BACK.

05:37.870 --> 05:40.668
Tituba: THERE IS NO PLACE
FOR THAT CHILD IN SALEM.

05:40.700 --> 05:45.501
GEORGE SIBLEY DROVE JOHN ALDEN
OFF TO DIE IN THE WAR.

05:45.540 --> 05:47.337
WHAT DO YOU THINK
HE'S GONNA DO TO YOU

05:47.380 --> 05:51.339
WHEN HE FINDS OUT YOU'RE
PREGNANT WITH JOHN'S BABY?

05:51.380 --> 05:54.838
DO NOT FEAR THE WOODS.

05:54.880 --> 05:57.348
THE WOODS ARE GONNA
TAKE CARE OF THAT LITI'LE SOUL...

05:57.390 --> 05:59.711
AND YOU.

06:08.730 --> 06:11.528
Mary:
WHAT IS THIS PLACE?

06:11.570 --> 06:13.993
Tituba: YOU WANT TO LIVE?
LIE STILL.

06:14.040 --> 06:17.009
Mary: [ GASPING ]
PLEASE.

06:17.040 --> 06:18.701
IT'S ALL THAT I HAVE LEFI'
OF HIM.

06:18.740 --> 06:20.230
Tituba: HUSH.

06:35.260 --> 06:37.922
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

06:43.100 --> 06:45.318
[ OWL HOOTS ]

06:52.980 --> 06:54.607
Mary: [ GASPING ]

07:04.090 --> 07:06.081
[ GASPS ] NO, WAIT.
I-I-I DON'T WANT TO DO THIS.

07:06.120 --> 07:08.088
Tituba: YOU DON'T
HAVE A CHOICE, MARY.

07:08.120 --> 07:09.656
Mary: PLEASE.

07:09.690 --> 07:11.658
-Tituba: THIS IS WHAT YOU WANT.
-Mary: PLEASE.

07:11.690 --> 07:13.089
Tituba:
THIS IS WHAT YOU WANT.

07:13.130 --> 07:14.222
Mary: [Weakly] NO...PLEASE.

07:14.260 --> 07:15.249
Tituba: LET HIM IN.

07:25.540 --> 07:26.609
Mary: [ CHUCKLES]

07:26.640 --> 07:28.631
NO, PLEASE.

07:28.680 --> 07:30.500
[ WHIMPERING ]
STAY THERE!

07:30.550 --> 07:31.778
[ SCREAMS ]

07:34.320 --> 07:35.673
[ GASPS ]

07:53.040 --> 07:55.634
JOHN. JOHN.
JOHN, HELP ME.

07:55.670 --> 07:57.365
HELP ME!

07:57.410 --> 07:59.332
[ GASPS, SCREAMS ]

07:59.370 --> 08:00.530
Tituba:
NOW TELL HIM.

08:00.580 --> 08:03.504
SAY IT.
THIS IS WHAT YOU WANT.

08:03.550 --> 08:05.199
Mary: YES. YES!

08:05.250 --> 08:06.774
YES!

08:06.820 --> 08:10.347
AAH!

08:11.990 --> 08:14.686
[ GASPS ]

08:25.430 --> 08:27.432
[ WHIMPERS ]

08:31.740 --> 08:33.935
[ SCREAMS ]

08:37.180 --> 08:40.013
[ SOBBING ]

08:40.050 --> 08:44.248
Tituba: ALL THE WORLD
SHALL BE YOURS IN RETURN.

08:44.290 --> 08:47.054
ALL THE WORLD.

08:54.100 --> 08:56.898
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

08:58.630 --> 09:00.632
[ DOG BARKS, BIRDS CHIRPING ]

09:23.390 --> 09:25.381
[ HORSE NEIGHS,
INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS]

09:41.410 --> 09:44.902
Man: ...FROM HEAVEN
IN FLAMING FIRE,

09:44.950 --> 09:47.748
TAKING VENGEANCE UPON
ALL THOSE WHO KNOW NOT GOD,

09:47.780 --> 09:49.077
WHO HAVE DISOBEYED THE GOSPEL!

09:49.120 --> 09:50.212
Man #2:
READ FOR YOURSELF THE TRUTH.

09:50.250 --> 09:51.478
THE TERRIBLE TRUTH --

09:51.520 --> 09:54.717
WITCHES AMONG US,
THE DEVIL IN SALEM.

09:54.760 --> 09:56.489
FOR YOU, SIR.

09:57.860 --> 09:59.054
FOR YOU, SIR.

09:59.090 --> 10:01.752
Man #3: NO.

10:08.170 --> 10:10.468
[ MEN GRUNTING ]

10:15.710 --> 10:18.372
Man: EASY. EASY.

10:34.830 --> 10:37.867
[ LOCK CLICKS ]

10:59.520 --> 11:00.782
[ RIFLE COCKS ]

11:00.820 --> 11:03.152
Giles:
THIS IS THE ALDEN HOUSE,

11:03.190 --> 11:06.353
AND THERE AIN'T ANY ALDENS LEFI'.

11:06.390 --> 11:11.123
SO YOU ARE EITHER A GHOST,
OR YOU'RE ABOUT TO BE ONE.

11:11.170 --> 11:14.492
John: THAT'S A HARSH WAY
TO SAY "WELCOME HOME."

11:14.540 --> 11:16.292
Giles: JOHNNY?

11:16.340 --> 11:17.830
CAN'T BE.

11:17.870 --> 11:20.839
I HEARD YOU WAS DEAD --
KILLED IN THE WAR.

11:20.880 --> 11:22.973
John: I WISHED I WAS
A COUPLE OF TIMES.

11:23.010 --> 11:26.548
Giles: AH, WELL,
THEY CAN'T KEEP A GOOD MAN DOWN.

11:28.350 --> 11:29.988
[ SACK THUDS ]

11:30.020 --> 11:31.544
[ CRUNCH ]

11:31.590 --> 11:33.182
[ CHUCKLES ]

11:33.220 --> 11:35.518
John: SAW THREE MEN STRUNG UP
ON THE WAY INTO TOWN

11:35.560 --> 11:37.721
AND A NEW GALLOWS BEING BUILT
IN THE HEART OF THE COMMON.

11:37.760 --> 11:39.523
WHAT THE HELL IS THAT?

11:39.560 --> 11:44.020
Giles: PRECIOUS SALEM CAUGHT UP
IN A STINKING WITCH PANIC.

11:44.070 --> 11:45.697
John: WITCH PANIC?

11:45.730 --> 11:48.528
WHO DID THE BIGWIGS SEND IN
TO PUT OUT THE FIRE,

11:48.570 --> 11:50.709
THE ALMIGHTY INCREASE MATHER?

11:50.740 --> 11:54.836
Giles:
NO, HIS SON -- COTTON.

11:54.880 --> 11:57.599
AND NOT A CHIP OFF THE OLD
BLOCK -- BARELY A SPLINTER.

11:57.650 --> 11:59.709
John:
I REMEMBER WHEN WE WERE KIDS

11:59.750 --> 12:01.342
HE USED TO DRESS LIKE A GIRL.

12:01.380 --> 12:02.677
FOUGHT LIKE ONE, TOO.

12:02.720 --> 12:04.085
Giles:
WELL, HE'S ALL GROWED-UP NOW.

12:04.120 --> 12:07.419
A FINE FOOL
IN FINE SILK CLOTHES,

12:07.460 --> 12:09.587
AND NOT JUST ANY FOOL,
THE MOST DANGEROUS KIND --

12:09.620 --> 12:11.429
THE KIND THAT THINKS
HE KNOWS EVERYTHING.

12:11.460 --> 12:15.191
BUT YOU DIDN'T COME BACK
FOR ALL THIS HORSESHIT.

12:15.230 --> 12:19.098
YOU COME BACK FOR ONE THING
AND ONE THING ONLY.

12:19.130 --> 12:23.863
TRUTH TOLD,
SHE'S FINER THAN EVER.

12:23.910 --> 12:26.561
AND SHE'S THE RICHEST WOMAN
IN SALEM.

12:26.610 --> 12:28.578
AND WHY NOT?

12:28.610 --> 12:31.340
SHE'S MARY SIBLEY NOW.

12:49.700 --> 12:52.828
John: SIBLEY?

12:52.870 --> 12:54.167
GEORGE SIBLEY.

12:54.200 --> 12:55.599
BUT HIS WIFE --

12:55.640 --> 12:58.962
Giles:
DIED A FEW YEARS AGO.

12:59.010 --> 13:01.274
YOU'VE BEEN GONE
A LONG TIME, JOHN.

13:06.480 --> 13:08.448
KEEP YOUR POWDER IN YOUR BAG.

13:08.480 --> 13:10.311
ONE DAY,

13:10.350 --> 13:14.480
YOUR MARY WILL BE THE RICHEST
WIDOW IN THE COUNTRY.

13:20.330 --> 13:23.493
Nathaniel:
THE DRIVER'S AT THE DOOR

13:23.530 --> 13:25.361
WITH SOME PACKAGES
FOR YOU, MA'AM.

13:25.400 --> 13:27.038
Mary: SEND HIM IN.

13:27.070 --> 13:30.460
AND, NATHANIEL,
TAKE MR. SIBLEY WITH YOU.

13:30.510 --> 13:33.229
TIME FOR HIS BATH.

13:44.320 --> 13:47.778
NOW, ISAAC,
TELL ME SOME NEWS OF THE WORLD.

13:47.820 --> 13:50.948
Isaac: SAW A DUSTY FELLA
WALKING INTO TOWN TODAY.

13:50.990 --> 13:53.197
I COULDN'T BELIEVE MY EYES.

13:53.230 --> 13:54.322
Mary: WHY?

13:54.360 --> 13:56.191
Isaac:
IT WAS JOHN ALDEN.

13:56.230 --> 13:58.721
Mary: [ GASPS ]

14:09.040 --> 14:11.144
[ LAUGHTER ]

14:11.180 --> 14:14.377
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

14:14.420 --> 14:16.376
Lamb: WELCOME BACK,
REVEREND MATHER.

14:16.420 --> 14:18.581
RUM, GIN, ALE?

14:18.620 --> 14:22.078
Cotton: YES.

14:22.120 --> 14:24.122
[ BOTTLES CLINK ]

14:31.470 --> 14:32.767
[ MUG THUDS]

14:32.800 --> 14:34.438
[ SIGHS ]

14:34.470 --> 14:36.938
I NEED THREE STRONG MEN.

14:36.970 --> 14:38.232
[ COINS CLINK ]

14:38.270 --> 14:41.706
I CAN PAY.

14:41.740 --> 14:43.776
John: FOR WHAT?

14:43.810 --> 14:46.779
Cotton:
TO SUBDUE A GIRL.

14:59.960 --> 15:01.928
REVEREND LEWIS.

15:01.960 --> 15:03.894
Lewis:
PLEASE HELP MY DAUGHTER.

15:03.930 --> 15:05.761
AND BE CAREFUL.

15:14.510 --> 15:16.899
[ WOMAN SOBBING ]

15:16.950 --> 15:18.941
[ WOOD CREAKING ]

15:23.320 --> 15:25.515
[ LATCH CLICKS ]

15:41.670 --> 15:43.535
Mercy:
[ SCREAMING ]

15:45.340 --> 15:48.207
Cotton: TIE HER DOWN!

15:49.180 --> 15:50.909
TIE HER DOWN!!

15:50.950 --> 15:52.349
Mercy:
[ GROANING, SCREAMING ]

15:56.150 --> 15:58.744
[ GASPING ]

15:58.790 --> 16:01.679
[ Sobbing ] PLEASE, I BEG YOU,
SIR. PLEASE, MAKE THIS STOP.

16:01.720 --> 16:05.019
Cotton: I CAN DO NOTHING, MERCY,
UNLESS YOU TELL ME...

16:05.060 --> 16:07.199
WHO IS IT TORMENTS YOU?

16:07.230 --> 16:09.255
Mercy:
S-SHE'S RIGHT THERE.

16:09.300 --> 16:11.165
Cotton: "SHE"?

16:11.200 --> 16:12.963
WHO IS HERE?

16:13.000 --> 16:14.797
MERCY, YOU MUST TELL ME!

16:14.840 --> 16:16.296
WHO IS IN THIS ROOM WITH US?!

16:16.340 --> 16:18.638
Mercy:
THE HAG! THE OLD WOMAN!

16:18.670 --> 16:20.137
SHE'S STANDING RIGHT THERE!

16:20.180 --> 16:22.330
PLEASE.

16:22.380 --> 16:23.472
[ SOBBING ]

16:25.050 --> 16:26.472
Cotton:
A SIMPLE PHYSIC.

16:26.510 --> 16:28.478
-Mercy: [ GASPING ]
-Cotton: TO SLEEP.

16:28.520 --> 16:30.511
Mercy: [ STAMMERS ]

16:37.690 --> 16:40.488
PLEASE. PLEASE.

16:40.530 --> 16:42.395
[ STAMMERS ]

16:46.700 --> 16:48.793
Cotton: WE CALL IT
A SPECTRAL ATTACK --

16:48.840 --> 16:51.058
THE WORK OF WITCHES.

16:51.110 --> 16:52.702
PRAY FOR HER.

16:52.740 --> 16:54.708
John: I CALL BULLSHIT.

16:54.740 --> 16:57.538
SHE'S CLEARLY
TOUCHED IN THE HEAD.

16:57.580 --> 17:01.414
SHE NEEDS A DOCTOR,
NOT YOUR PRAYERS.

17:17.600 --> 17:20.364
[ FLOOR CREAKING ]

17:23.370 --> 17:26.203
Mercy: [ GASPING ]

17:28.210 --> 17:30.178
[ SCREAMING ]

17:37.550 --> 17:39.609
[ BELLS TOLLING ]

17:39.650 --> 17:41.686
Mrs. Hale:
DON'T DAWDLE, CHILD.

17:41.720 --> 17:43.529
I WANT YOU IN THE FRONT ROW

17:43.560 --> 17:46.927
WHERE COTI'ON MATHER CAN'T HELP
BUT BE DAZZLED BY YOUR CHARMS.

17:46.960 --> 17:48.757
Anne:
FOR HEAVEN'S SAKE, MOTHER,

17:48.800 --> 17:53.191
WHY NOT JUST WRAP ME IN SILK AND
PARADE ME ON THE AUCTION BLOCK?

17:53.240 --> 17:55.561
[ HORSE NEIGHS ]

18:02.740 --> 18:05.641
Cotton:
FEAR NO MAN'S WAR.

18:05.680 --> 18:09.218
FOR ONLY A WAR FROM HELL
COULD DESTROY SALEM.

18:09.250 --> 18:13.311
THE DEVIL
WAS NEVER GOING TO LET

18:13.360 --> 18:15.817
A PROMISED LAND BE BUILT HERE

18:19.990 --> 18:22.220
AND WITCHES
ARMED WITH DEADLY MALICE

18:22.260 --> 18:24.899
ARE THE MOST
MALIGNANT AND INSIDIOUS WEAPONS

18:24.930 --> 18:26.898
IN THAT BATTLE...

18:26.930 --> 18:29.728
IN THAT WAR.

18:29.770 --> 18:31.567
EVEN A SINGLE WITCH IN SALEM
IS ENOUGH TO DESTROY

18:31.610 --> 18:35.239
EVERYTHING WE HAVE BUILT
AND EVER HOPE TO BUILD HERE!

18:35.280 --> 18:39.899
NOW, WE HAVE ALREADY
KILLED THREE OF THEM,

18:39.950 --> 18:42.919
AND YET THEIR MALICE
CONTINUES UNABATED.

18:42.950 --> 18:45.111
WHY?

18:45.150 --> 18:47.948
BECAUSE THERE ARE STILL
WITCHES HERE AMONG US!

18:47.990 --> 18:50.925
[ GASPING, MURMURING ]

18:50.960 --> 18:53.155
PERHAPS IN THIS VERY HALL!

18:56.230 --> 19:00.690
IMAGINE A FOE YOU CAN'T SEE
ARMED WITH WEAPONS UNKNOWN

19:00.740 --> 19:03.459
AND THE ABILITY TO APPEAR
AS ANY ONE OF US!

19:03.510 --> 19:07.332
Mr. Hale: THEN HOW CAN YOU HOPE
TO IDENTIFY THE CORRECT CULPRIT?

19:09.480 --> 19:11.778
Cotton:
HAVE YOU SEEN THE GIRL, SIR?

19:11.810 --> 19:16.213
EVEN NOW, MERCY LEWIS
BLEEDS FROM 100 WOUNDS --

19:16.250 --> 19:20.209
SOME IMPOSSIBLE TO SELF-INFLICT.

19:20.260 --> 19:23.058
SHE IS THE ONE WHO WILL TELL US
WHO DOES THIS.

19:23.090 --> 19:24.728
Mr. Hale: I SEE.

19:24.760 --> 19:26.887
THE RAVINGS OF A POOR, SICK GIRL

19:26.930 --> 19:31.469
WILL HELP YOU IDENTIFY WHAT
YOUR REASON FAILS TO DELIVER.

19:31.500 --> 19:32.899
Cotton: MY FATHER --

19:32.930 --> 19:36.991
Mr. Hale: YES, OF COURSE.
YOUR FATHER.

19:37.040 --> 19:41.170
DID YOUR FATHER,
WHOM WE ALL SO RESPECT,

19:41.210 --> 19:43.849
OFFER YOU ANY ADVICE
WHEN HE SENT YOU IN HIS STEAD

19:43.880 --> 19:44.949
TO OUR AID?

19:47.110 --> 19:50.045
Cotton:
HE...ADVISED CAUTION.

19:50.080 --> 19:52.344
Mr. Hale: CAUTION?

19:52.390 --> 19:56.508
AND ARE WE TO TAKE
THREE PEOPLE HUNG

19:56.560 --> 20:00.849
AS THE MEASURE
OF MATHER JUNIOR'S CAUTION?

20:00.900 --> 20:04.199
THERE COULD BE NOTHING
WORSE FOR SALEM,

20:04.230 --> 20:06.698
FOR THE COUNTRY,
THAN A WITCH HUNT.

20:06.730 --> 20:10.063
George: [ GAGGING ]

20:12.970 --> 20:15.507
[ MURMURS]

20:15.540 --> 20:17.007
WITCH ES.

20:17.040 --> 20:20.271
WITCH ES.

20:20.320 --> 20:22.174
Mary: INDEED.

20:22.220 --> 20:26.839
AS MY BELOVED HUSBAND, THE HEAD
OF YOUR SELECTMEN, REMINDS ME,

20:26.890 --> 20:30.189
THERE IS SOMETHING WORSE
THAN A WITCH HUNT --

20:30.220 --> 20:31.426
A WITCH.

20:31.460 --> 20:33.223
John: A WITCH?

20:33.260 --> 20:34.796
[ CONGREGATION GASPS ]

20:34.830 --> 20:37.526
SURE, THAT'S BAD.

20:37.570 --> 20:39.128
BUT WHY NOT AN OGRE...

20:39.170 --> 20:41.889
OR A GOBLIN?

20:41.940 --> 20:45.637
WHY NOT A DRAGON, LONG AS
WE'RE TALKING ABOUT FAIRY TALES?

20:45.670 --> 20:47.809
Mary: JOHN ALDEN.

20:47.840 --> 20:51.901
WE ALL WELCOME CAPTAIN ALDEN
HOME FROM HIS LONG,

20:51.950 --> 20:55.613
LONG SERVICE IN OUR DEFENSE.

21:00.150 --> 21:02.084
Giles: PURITANS KNOW
THEIR SUN IS SETTING.

21:02.120 --> 21:04.054
NOTHING LIKE A NEW ENEMY
OR A NEW OLD ENEMY

21:04.090 --> 21:06.558
TO GET PEOPLE BEHIND YOU.

21:06.590 --> 21:09.650
Mary: CAPTAIN ALDEN.

21:09.700 --> 21:12.225
John: MRS. SIBLEY.

21:12.270 --> 21:14.238
Mary: MR. SIBLEY AND I

21:14.270 --> 21:16.397
ARE HOSTING
A SMALL DINNER TOMORROW NIGHT.

21:16.440 --> 21:17.839
WE'D BE HONORED IF YOU'D JOIN.

21:23.110 --> 21:25.101
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

21:44.570 --> 21:45.992
[ GUN COCKS ]

21:46.030 --> 21:47.861
John:
WHY ARE YOU STARING AT ME?

21:47.900 --> 21:51.301
I DON'T EVEN KNOW YOU.

21:56.580 --> 21:57.706
ISAAC?

21:57.750 --> 22:00.310
Isaac:
ISAAC THE FORNICATOR.

22:00.350 --> 22:01.772
HIDE YOUR WIVES.

22:01.820 --> 22:03.879
HIDE YOUR DAUGHTERS.
HELL, YOUR SHEEP!

22:06.420 --> 22:08.388
SO, WHAT DO YOU WANT FROM ME?

22:08.420 --> 22:11.389
Isaac:
LISTEN TO ME, JOHN ALDEN.

22:11.430 --> 22:13.455
COMING HOME TO SALEM
TO GET OUT OF THE WAR

22:13.500 --> 22:15.923
IS LIKE JUMPING IN THE OCEAN
TO GET OUT OF THE RAIN.

22:17.330 --> 22:19.969
TRUTH HIDES.

22:20.000 --> 22:21.865
THEY COULD BE ANYONE.

22:21.900 --> 22:24.061
John: OH, THEY WHO?
WHO'S THEY?

22:24.110 --> 22:25.099
Isaac: WITCHES!

22:30.110 --> 22:31.372
AIN'T NO FAIRY TALE.

22:31.410 --> 22:33.878
THEY'RE REAL.

22:40.090 --> 22:41.387
John: [ GRUNTS ]

22:41.420 --> 22:43.388
Isaac:
ALL THESE YEARS,

22:43.430 --> 22:46.422
YOUR MARY'S THE ONLY ONE
WHO'S EVER DONE ME A GOOD TURN.

22:46.460 --> 22:49.850
John:
SHE'S NOT MY MARY NOW.

22:49.900 --> 22:53.529
Isaac:
YOU LEFI' ONCE BEFORE.

22:53.570 --> 22:54.832
LOOK WHAT HAPPENED.

22:54.870 --> 22:57.862
DON'T WALK OUT ON US AGAIN.

23:19.090 --> 23:22.423
Cotton: [ SIGHS ]

23:24.100 --> 23:27.558
Lewis:
IS THIS REALLY NECESSARY?

23:27.600 --> 23:30.239
Cotton:
A WITCH ES' FAMILIARS --

23:30.270 --> 23:34.730
DEMONS, USUALLY IN THE FORM
OF AN ANIMAL.

23:34.780 --> 23:37.647
CAT, RAT, A BIRD, OR A TOAD --

23:37.680 --> 23:40.649
THEY PERFORM
ALL SORTS OF USEFUL TASKS

23:40.680 --> 23:43.478
AS LONG AS THEY'RE FED.

23:43.520 --> 23:45.647
YOU HEARD WHAT SHE TOLD US.

23:45.690 --> 23:47.715
SHE WAS FORCED
TO FEED THEIR FAMILIARS.

23:47.760 --> 23:50.752
SHE MUST BE SEARCHED
FOR THE MARKS --

23:50.790 --> 23:54.726
TEATS WHERE SHE SUCKLED THEM.

23:54.760 --> 23:59.094
Lewis: [GASPS]
PLEASE HELP HER.

23:59.130 --> 24:00.358
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

24:19.290 --> 24:21.758
Cotton:
[ BREATHING HEAVILY]

24:21.790 --> 24:24.452
[ TAPPING ]

24:24.490 --> 24:27.084
[ POUNDING ]

24:27.130 --> 24:30.588
"WOE TO THE INHABITANTS
OF THE EARTH AND OF THE SEA!

24:30.630 --> 24:33.997
"FOR THE DEVIL HAS COME DOWN
UNTO YOU WITH GREAT WRATH

24:34.040 --> 24:37.532
BECAUSE HE KNOWETH
THAT HE HATH BUT A SHORT TIME."

24:37.570 --> 24:39.003
[ SIGHS ]

24:39.040 --> 24:41.508
REVELATIONS 12: 12.

24:41.540 --> 24:43.770
Gloriana:
I SEE THE END OF THE WORLD

24:43.810 --> 24:45.209
URGES YOU ONTO GREATER EFFORTS.

24:45.250 --> 24:46.672
Cotton:
MM, AS IT MUST US ALL.

24:46.710 --> 24:48.519
Gloriana: OUR GRANNY
USED TO SCARE US SILLY

24:48.550 --> 24:50.177
WITH THOSE WITCH STORIES.

24:50.220 --> 24:52.518
BUT SHE'D REALLY
TERRIFY MY BROTHERS.

24:52.550 --> 24:55.189
SHE TOLD THEM WITCHES
COULD STEAL A MAN'S --

24:55.220 --> 24:56.187
Cotton: AAH!
[ LAUGHS ]

24:56.220 --> 24:57.551
Gloriana: [ LAUGHS ]

24:57.590 --> 24:59.524
Cotton:
WOULD YOU LIKE THAT, GLORIANA,

24:59.560 --> 25:02.290
WITHOUT THE BOTHER
OF THE MAN ATTACHED?

25:02.330 --> 25:03.991
[ PANTING ]

25:04.030 --> 25:06.965
Gloriana: NOT THIS MAN.

25:07.000 --> 25:08.137
Cotton: [ GASPS ]

25:08.170 --> 25:09.637
[ WOMEN CHUCKLING ]

25:09.670 --> 25:12.901
Man: MY DARLING.

25:12.940 --> 25:16.103
Mab:
SEE YOU NEXT TIME, GOVERNOR.

25:18.180 --> 25:20.171
Cotton: [ SIGHS ]

25:22.750 --> 25:24.718
JUST ATTENDING TO THE POOR.

25:24.750 --> 25:29.050
John: NO DOUBT --
AND THE POOR IN SPIRIT.

25:29.090 --> 25:32.218
Cotton:
CAPTAIN ALDEN, RIGHT?

25:32.260 --> 25:34.922
I HAVEN'T SEEN YOU
SINCE WE WERE CHILDREN.

25:36.430 --> 25:39.069
I EXPECTED TO SEE YOU
UP AT HARVARD.

25:39.100 --> 25:43.059
SURPRISED TO HEAR THAT YOU'D
RUN OFF TO JOIN THE MILITIA --

25:43.100 --> 25:45.068
LIKE A SERVANT.

25:45.110 --> 25:46.566
John: I WOULD HAVE LOVED
TO SPEND FOUR YEARS

25:46.610 --> 25:48.407
COUNTING ANGELS
ON THE HEADS OF PINS, BUT...

25:48.440 --> 25:49.577
Cotton: HMM.

25:49.610 --> 25:51.578
John:
...THERE WAS A WAR ON.

25:51.610 --> 25:53.168
Cotton: PITY.

25:53.210 --> 25:55.576
I OWE EVERYTHING
TO MY EDUCATION.

25:55.620 --> 25:58.180
John: TAUGHT YOU EVERYTHING
ABOUT HUNTING WITCHES?

25:58.220 --> 25:59.585
Cotton: NO.

25:59.620 --> 26:02.350
BUT MY FATHER BURNT SCORES
BACK IN ESSEX,

26:02.390 --> 26:05.689
AND I'VE READ EVERY BOOK
THERE IS ON THE SUBJECT --

26:05.730 --> 26:08.028
IN EIGHT LANGUAGES.

26:08.060 --> 26:11.461
John: SO, YOU LEARNED
YOUR HUNTING FROM BOOKS.

26:11.500 --> 26:15.197
WELL, THAT'S A BIT LIKE
LEARNING THE FACTS OF LIFE

26:15.240 --> 26:16.730
FROM YOUR MAIDEN AUNT.

26:16.770 --> 26:18.362
BUT NEVER MIND.

26:18.410 --> 26:20.970
YOU'RE HERE NOW, AND
YOU'RE THE EXPERT ON WITCHES,

26:21.010 --> 26:23.171
SO LET ME ASK YOU.

26:25.780 --> 26:29.568
WHAT DO THESE AWFUL WITCHES
WANT, HUH?

26:29.620 --> 26:31.781
Cotton:
THE SAME THING WE ALL WANT...

26:33.450 --> 26:36.954
...A COUNTRY OF THEIR OWN.

26:39.260 --> 26:43.253
John: AND HERE I'VE BEEN WASTING
MY TIME FIGHTING MERE INDIANS.

26:44.670 --> 26:47.161
GOOD NIGHT, HARVARD.

26:52.840 --> 26:55.832
George: [ GROANING ]

27:10.620 --> 27:13.282
Mary:
TIME FOR YOUR FEEDING.

27:14.900 --> 27:17.528
George: [ GRUNTS ]

27:17.560 --> 27:19.562
Mary: [ GRUNTING ]

27:23.200 --> 27:25.998
[ STOMACH GURGLING ]

27:26.040 --> 27:27.871
George: [ GROANS ]

27:29.080 --> 27:30.775
Mary: YES.

27:30.810 --> 27:34.109
YES.

27:34.150 --> 27:35.708
[ CLICKS TONGUE ]

27:35.750 --> 27:37.342
YES.

27:42.760 --> 27:44.523
[ CLICKS TONGUE ]

27:48.230 --> 27:51.563
George: SOMEONE, HELP ME!

27:51.600 --> 27:53.192
[Weakly] HELP ME.

27:53.230 --> 27:56.495
Mary: YES.

27:56.540 --> 27:58.007
George: NO.

27:58.040 --> 27:59.667
HELP ME! HELP!

27:59.710 --> 28:02.008
HELP!
[ GAGGING ]

28:05.750 --> 28:08.071
Mary:
GEORGE, DON'T FIGHT IT.

28:09.420 --> 28:11.388
YOU KNOW IT ONLY HURTS MORE.

28:11.420 --> 28:13.411
George: [ GRUNTING ]

28:15.260 --> 28:21.051
Mary: YOU TOOK AWAY EVERYTHING
I HAD, GEORGE SIBLEY...

28:21.100 --> 28:25.389
EVERYTHING I LOVED.

28:25.430 --> 28:29.161
CAN YOU IMAGINE
HOW GOOD IT FEELS

28:29.200 --> 28:32.499
TO TAKE EVERYTHING YOU HAVE,

28:32.540 --> 28:35.179
DESTROY ALL YOU'VE BUILT,

28:35.210 --> 28:37.849
AND DEVOUR YOUR VERY SOUL?

28:37.880 --> 28:41.008
George: [ WHIMPERS ]

28:41.050 --> 28:42.415
Mary: ALL DONE.

28:42.450 --> 28:44.338
George: [ GRUNTS ]

28:54.430 --> 28:55.954
[ BELLS TOLLING ]

28:56.000 --> 28:57.558
Mr. Hale: IWOULD LIKE
TO MAKE A TOAST TO OUR HOSTESS,

28:57.600 --> 28:58.794
MARY SIBLEY,

28:58.830 --> 29:00.388
WHO HAS SHOWN US

29:00.430 --> 29:03.194
THAT TRUE PIETY AND TRUE BEAUTY

29:03.240 --> 29:04.969
AMOUNT TO THE SAME WORSHIP.

29:05.010 --> 29:06.602
Cotton: INDEED.

29:06.640 --> 29:08.972
BEAUTY
IS THE LAST MIRACLE ALLOWED

29:09.010 --> 29:10.375
IN AN UGLY...

29:10.410 --> 29:12.105
FALLEN WORLD.

29:12.150 --> 29:14.971
Mrs. Hale: MAGISTRATE HALE
AND I ARE CONCERNED

29:15.020 --> 29:18.285
ABOUT OUR DAUGHTER'S
INNER BEAUTY, REVEREND MATHER.

29:18.320 --> 29:21.619
PERHAPS YOU COULD SUGGEST
A TUTOR FOR HER,

29:21.660 --> 29:23.616
A HARVARD MAN --
LIKE YOURSELF?

29:23.660 --> 29:27.118
Anne: I BELIEVE THERE IS ONLY SO
MUCH YOU CAN LEARN FROM BOOKS.

29:27.160 --> 29:29.424
EXPERIENCE IS OUR TRUE TEACHER.

29:29.460 --> 29:31.291
DON'T YOU AGREE, CAPTAIN ALDEN?

29:33.330 --> 29:35.798
John: WELL, THAT DEPENDS
ON THE EXPERIENCE.

29:35.840 --> 29:38.832
Anne: YOURS MUST HAVE BEEN
FASCINATING -- WITH THE INDIANS.

29:38.870 --> 29:41.100
THEY'RE SO MYSTERIOUS,

29:41.140 --> 29:42.937
SO. . .NATURAL.

29:42.980 --> 29:44.470
Mrs. Hale: NATURAL?

29:44.510 --> 29:46.649
[ SCOFFS ]
"UNNATURAL," I'D SAY.

29:46.680 --> 29:48.648
SOULLESS SAVAGES.

29:48.680 --> 29:51.478
John: I ASSURE YOU, MA'AM,
THE INDIANS DO HAVE SOULS,

29:51.520 --> 29:53.147
IF ANY OF US DO.

29:55.220 --> 29:57.381
-Cotton: "IF"?
-Anne: [ LAUGHS]

29:58.730 --> 30:01.699
Mary:
AND WHAT ABOUT WITCHES?

30:01.730 --> 30:04.028
DO THEY HAVE SOULS, TOO?

30:04.070 --> 30:06.026
-George: [ GRUNTING ]
-Cotton: THEY DO.

30:06.070 --> 30:09.335
BUT THEY HAVE DEEDED THEM
TO THE DEVIL HIMSELF

30:09.370 --> 30:14.171
IN EXCHANGE FOR POWERS
AND ALL THAT THEY DESIRE.

30:14.210 --> 30:16.201
-Mary: A CONTRACT?
-Cotton: INDEED.

30:16.240 --> 30:17.776
Mary: IRONIC,

30:17.810 --> 30:19.209
AS I BELIEVE, BY LAW,

30:19.250 --> 30:21.013
A WOMAN'S NOT ALLOWED
TO ENTER A CONTRACT

30:21.050 --> 30:22.813
BUT THROUGH THE AGENCY
OF THEIR HUSBAND.

30:22.850 --> 30:25.216
-George: [ COUGHS, GAGS ]
-Mary: NATHANIEL.

30:25.250 --> 30:26.478
Nathaniel: YES, MA'AM.

30:26.520 --> 30:28.317
Cotton: NOT ALL WITCHES
ARE WOMEN.

30:28.360 --> 30:30.214
Anne: AND WHAT DO YOU THINK,
CAPTAIN ALDEN?

30:31.890 --> 30:33.357
John: I DON'T KNOW.
[ SIGHS ]

30:33.390 --> 30:37.019
I THINK SOME THINGS
JUST BEGGAR BELIEF,

30:37.060 --> 30:41.565
LIKE AN HONEST FRENCHMAN
OR A FAITHFUL WOMAN,

30:41.600 --> 30:45.229
THINGS THAT I'LL BELIEVE IN
IF AND WHEN I SEE ONE.

30:45.270 --> 30:46.532
Mr. Hale:
I FIND I WORRY MORE

30:46.570 --> 30:48.674
ABOUT THE FRENCH
AND THE INDIAN ATTACKS

30:48.710 --> 30:50.632
THAN I DO WITCHES.

30:50.680 --> 30:52.807
WHAT'S YOUR OPINION,
CAPTAIN ALDEN?

30:52.850 --> 30:55.171
JUST HOW VULNERABLE ARE WE?

30:55.220 --> 30:58.280
John: MM.

31:12.130 --> 31:14.462
Mary: ARE YOU ALL RIGHT,
CAPTAIN ALDEN?

31:19.910 --> 31:23.869
John: I THINK THIS RICH FOOD
DOESN'T AGREE WITH ME.

31:23.910 --> 31:26.549
Mary:
SOME FRESH AIR MIGHT HELP.

31:26.580 --> 31:29.572
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

31:41.260 --> 31:43.694
I WAS TOLD YOU WERE KILLED.

31:43.730 --> 31:48.360
John: WAS THAT BEFORE
OR AFTER YOU MARRIED SIBLEY?

31:48.400 --> 31:50.197
Mary:
I REMEMBER BEING TOLD ONCE

31:50.240 --> 31:53.869
THAT THE WAR
WOULDN'T LAST A YEAR.

31:53.910 --> 31:56.538
John:
THAT WASN'T UP TO ME.

31:56.580 --> 31:59.208
Mary:
I WAITED FOR YOU.

31:59.250 --> 32:03.539
YEARS AND YEARS WITHOUT A WORD.

32:03.580 --> 32:05.719
John: I COULDN'T WRITE.

32:05.750 --> 32:08.719
Mary: NO, OF COURSE NOT.

32:08.760 --> 32:11.058
TOO BUSY SAVING THE COUNTRY.

32:11.090 --> 32:14.719
John: NOT EXACTLY.

32:14.760 --> 32:17.092
I WAS CAPTURED.

32:24.610 --> 32:28.102
THEIR PRIEST MAN TOLD THE OTHERS
NOT TO TAKE THIS AWAY FROM ME.

32:29.610 --> 32:32.443
HE SAID THE UNIVERSE ITSELF
WAS MADE OUT OF VOWS,

32:32.480 --> 32:37.270
AND BREAKING THEM
CARRIES CONSEQUENCES.

32:37.320 --> 32:41.154
I KNOW THAT THIS
IS JUST HALF A SILVER COIN,

32:41.190 --> 32:44.557
AND YOU HAVE...
NO SHORTAGE OF SILVER NOW.

32:46.860 --> 32:50.648
MARY, COME WITH ME.

32:50.700 --> 32:54.329
NOW...TONIGHT.

32:54.370 --> 32:56.691
I HAVE MONEY IN A BANK
IN NEW YORK.

32:56.740 --> 32:58.332
IT'S DIFFERENT THERE.

32:58.370 --> 33:02.272
THERE'S NOT A PURITAN IN SIGHT.
IT'S NOT TOO LATE.

33:02.310 --> 33:05.507
WE CAN BE TOGETHER -- ANYWHERE.

33:05.550 --> 33:06.676
ANYWHERE BUT HERE.

33:06.710 --> 33:09.178
-Mary: NEW YORK?
-John: YEAH.

33:09.220 --> 33:11.381
Mary: IS THAT BEFORE OR AFTER
YOU WERE CAPTURED?

33:15.190 --> 33:19.149
YOU WALK OUT OF HERE ONE NIGHT,
AND YOU COME BACK YEARS LATER.

33:19.190 --> 33:20.657
A-AND YOU THINK THAT --

33:20.690 --> 33:21.998
John: MARY.

33:22.030 --> 33:23.349
Mary: [ SIGHS ]

33:32.410 --> 33:34.571
John: COME HERE.

33:42.280 --> 33:44.748
Mary: NO.

33:44.790 --> 33:46.985
I CAN'T.

33:47.020 --> 33:48.851
IT'S IMPOSSIBLE.

33:48.890 --> 33:50.357
HE'D NEVER LET ME.

33:50.390 --> 33:51.721
[ DOOR OPENS ]

33:51.760 --> 33:55.218
Mr. Hale:
NOW, NOW, MRS. SIBLEY.

33:55.260 --> 33:57.228
EVEN YOU HAVE NO RIGHT
TO MONOPOLIZE A GUEST

33:57.260 --> 34:01.560
AS FASCINATING AS CAPTAIN ALDEN,
FOR WHOM I HAVE A RARE GIl-T,

34:01.600 --> 34:05.229
A CIGAR OF TOBACCO
FROM GUYANA WITH SOME BRANDY.

34:05.270 --> 34:07.238
John:
I'M AFRAID ALL THIS...

34:07.270 --> 34:10.876
CIVILIZED EATING AND DRINKING
HAS LAID ME OUT, MAGISTRATE.

34:19.450 --> 34:21.452
Mary: [ SNIFFLES ]

34:25.830 --> 34:28.128
YOU TOLD ME HE WAS DEAD!

34:28.160 --> 34:29.798
Tituba: IT'S NOT LIKE
COUNTING SHEEP, HONEY.

34:29.830 --> 34:33.425
MORE LIKE COUNTING SHADOWS.

34:33.470 --> 34:35.131
BUT IT DON'T CHANGE A THING.

34:35.170 --> 34:40.904
WHAT'S JOHN ALDEN COMPARED
TO ALL THAT LIES BEFORE YOU?

34:40.940 --> 34:43.238
STOP YOUR WEEPING, WOMAN.

34:43.280 --> 34:45.578
THAT BOY DON'T DESERVE
THOSE TEARS.

34:45.610 --> 34:47.248
Mary:
THEY'RE NOT FOR HIM.

34:47.280 --> 34:49.077
THEY'RE FOR THE GIRL I ONCE WAS.

34:49.120 --> 34:51.213
Tituba: THAT GIRL BELONGS
TO SOMEBODY ELSE NOW.

34:51.250 --> 34:52.410
Mary:
[ SCREAMS, GASPS ]

34:54.690 --> 34:59.889
Tituba: WAS IT HE THAT LEl-T YOU
TO THE WOLVES?

34:59.930 --> 35:01.898
NO, CHILD.

35:01.930 --> 35:04.728
IT WAS HE THAT SAVED YOU
FROM THE WOLVES

35:04.770 --> 35:08.888
AND RAISED YOU UP
TO ALL OF THIS.

35:08.940 --> 35:13.058
YOU HAVE A GRAND VISION.

35:13.110 --> 35:15.977
DON'T LOSE SIGHT OF IT.

35:16.010 --> 35:20.276
TOMORROW, THE MOON IS WITH US.
TOMORROW, IT BEGINS.

35:20.310 --> 35:25.145
LEAVE YOUR ANGER AND YOUR PAIN
FOR THE KENAIMA TO FEED ON.

35:25.190 --> 35:27.841
HAS HE NOT BEEN TRUE TO HIS VOW?

35:27.890 --> 35:31.519
ARE NOT YOUR ENEMIES
NOW YOUR SLAVES?

35:31.560 --> 35:36.691
DO YOU NOT HAVE EVERYTHING
THAT YOU DESIRE --

35:36.730 --> 35:39.426
WEALTH, POWER?

35:39.470 --> 35:43.258
Mary: ALMOST EVERYTHING.

35:43.300 --> 35:44.631
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

35:45.910 --> 35:48.674
Man: PARDON ME, MA'AM.
A GENTLEMAN TO SEE YOU.

35:56.220 --> 35:59.041
Mary: MR. COREY.

35:59.090 --> 36:01.558
TO WHAT DO I OWE THE PLEASURE?

36:01.590 --> 36:05.378
Giles: I WAS WONDERING
IF I MIGHT TALK TO YOU, MA'AM.

36:08.400 --> 36:11.699
I HAD A SMALL FARM.

36:11.730 --> 36:14.836
FIRST, IT BROKE MY HEART.
THEN IT BROKE MY BACK.

36:14.870 --> 36:18.636
AS YOU AND I BOTH KNOW,
THE HEART HEALS.

36:18.670 --> 36:20.638
THE BACK NEVER DOES.

36:20.670 --> 36:22.638
I TOOK UP TRAPPING.

36:22.680 --> 36:25.899
IT'S A MEAGER LIVING --
RUINED THE INDIANS.

36:25.950 --> 36:28.418
NOW IT'S RUINING ME.

36:28.450 --> 36:33.183
THING ABOUT TRAPPING IS YOU
GET YOUR GOOD CATCH AT NIGHT.

36:33.220 --> 36:36.053
BUT BY MORNING,
IT'S SOMEONE ELSE'S MEAL.

36:36.090 --> 36:39.059
ME, I STAY WITH MY TRAPS.

36:39.090 --> 36:40.387
Mary: FASCINATING,
MR. COREY, BUT --

36:40.430 --> 36:42.648
Giles:
THAT'S WHY I WAS THERE...

36:42.700 --> 36:46.090
THE NIGHT YOU DID IT...

36:46.130 --> 36:48.860
YOU AND YOUR CINNAMON GIRL.

36:48.900 --> 36:51.664
Mary:
YOU WAITED A LONG TIME.

36:51.710 --> 36:54.008
Giles:
NOBODY'S BUSINESS TILL NOW.

36:54.040 --> 36:58.545
BUT THAT WAS JOHN ALDEN'S BABY
THAT YOU BURIED OUT THERE.

36:58.580 --> 37:03.517
AND THE WAY HE FEELS ABOUT YOU,
HE HAS A RIGHT TO KNOW.

37:03.550 --> 37:06.781
SO, ARE YOU GONNA TELL HIM?

37:06.820 --> 37:08.959
OR AM I?

37:12.390 --> 37:15.951
Anne:
OH, BLAST THIS WRETCHED THING.

37:16.000 --> 37:17.991
[ BELLS TOLLING ]

37:21.970 --> 37:23.597
John: THAT'S NOT BAD.

37:25.640 --> 37:28.939
Anne: REVEREND LEWIS
SAYS DRAWING IS IDOLATRY,

37:28.980 --> 37:31.744
LIKE WORSHIPING NATURE
OR SOMETHING.

37:31.780 --> 37:33.771
John: WELL, THERE MIGHT
BE WORSE THINGS TO WORSHIP.

37:38.020 --> 37:41.786
Anne:
I'D LIKE TO DRAW YOU SOMETIME.

37:43.760 --> 37:46.251
John: I'M NOT SURE I'D LIKE
TO SEE A PORTRAIT OF ME.

37:46.290 --> 37:47.382
Anne: [ LAUGHS ]

37:47.430 --> 37:48.624
John: [ CHUCKLES ]

37:48.660 --> 37:52.118
BESIDES, I HAVE NO TIME TO SIT.

37:52.170 --> 37:53.489
I'M ON WAY OUT OF TOWN.

37:55.340 --> 37:56.796
Anne: SO SOON?

37:56.840 --> 37:59.934
AFRAID OF WITCHES...

37:59.970 --> 38:01.938
OR BEING TAKEN FOR ONE?

38:01.980 --> 38:04.005
John:
IT'S A LONG WAY TO NEW YORK.

38:04.040 --> 38:05.678
GOOD DAY.

38:22.660 --> 38:23.957
Anne: [ GASPS ]

38:24.000 --> 38:25.763
Mary: OH, I DIDN'T MEAN
TO FRIGHTEN YOU.

38:25.800 --> 38:27.768
Anne:
OH, I'M NOT FRIGHTENED.

38:27.800 --> 38:29.768
[ SIGHS ]

38:29.800 --> 38:31.097
JUST SURPRISED.

38:31.140 --> 38:33.608
Mary:
YES, OF COURSE --

38:33.640 --> 38:35.779
A GIRL BRAVE ENOUGH
TO SKETCH IN A GRAVEYARD.

38:35.810 --> 38:38.699
Anne:
I'M NOT AFRAID OF THE DEAD,

38:38.750 --> 38:40.445
NOR THE LIVING FOR THAT MATTER.

38:40.480 --> 38:43.017
Mary: THAT'S BECAUSE
YOU KNOW NOTHING OF DEATH

38:43.050 --> 38:46.178
AND LESS OF LIFE.

38:46.220 --> 38:49.678
I COULD TEACH YOU --

38:49.720 --> 38:51.119
ABOUT LIFE...

38:51.160 --> 38:53.458
AND DEATH...

38:53.490 --> 38:56.493
AND MANY THINGS IN BETWEEN.

38:58.230 --> 39:01.859
DO YOU KNOW WHAT KILLED
NEARLY EVERY WOMAN BURIED HERE?

39:01.900 --> 39:03.868
LOVE.

39:03.900 --> 39:06.698
MOST DIED IN CHILDBIRTH.

39:06.740 --> 39:11.370
SO, LOVE IS TO A WOMAN
WHAT WAR IS TO A MAN --

39:11.410 --> 39:14.379
THE MOST DEADLY THING
THEY'LL DO.

39:14.420 --> 39:18.880
ONLY A FOOL RUNS QUICKLY
TO WAR OR LOVE.

39:18.920 --> 39:21.388
YOU'D BEST WATCH YOURSELF.

39:23.060 --> 39:27.019
Anne:
THANK YOU...MRS. SIBLEY.

39:27.060 --> 39:30.552
I CAN ONLY ASPIRE
TO YOUR HAPPY WISDOM.

39:46.650 --> 39:49.118
Cotton:
WHERE DO THE WITCHES MEET?

39:49.150 --> 39:52.119
Mercy: IN THE WOODS.

39:52.150 --> 39:53.947
Cotton: HOW MANY?

39:53.990 --> 39:56.356
Mercy: I DON'T KNOW.

39:56.390 --> 39:59.848
Cotton: WHO ARE THEY?

39:59.890 --> 40:02.859
Mercy: I -- [ SIGHS ]

40:02.900 --> 40:06.199
I CAN'T SEE THEIR FACES.

40:06.230 --> 40:09.028
LIKE THERE'S
THESE HEADS OF ANIMALS

40:09.070 --> 40:12.107
LIKE A STAG AND A PIG
AND A WOLF.

40:12.140 --> 40:14.301
Cotton:
BUT YOU KNOW WHO THEY ARE?

40:18.180 --> 40:20.478
Mercy:
[ Whimpering ] YES.

40:20.510 --> 40:21.738
YES.

40:21.780 --> 40:23.475
Cotton: THEIR NAM ES.

40:23.520 --> 40:24.544
Mercy: [ GASPS ]

40:24.590 --> 40:25.989
[ BABBLING ]

40:26.020 --> 40:28.045
Cotton: WHY WON'T YOU TELL ME
THEIR NAMES?

40:28.090 --> 40:29.717
Mercy:
[ Crying ] SHE WON'T LET ME.

40:29.760 --> 40:30.954
Cotton: "SHE"?

40:30.990 --> 40:32.127
-Mercy: YES.
-Cotton: WHO?

40:32.160 --> 40:34.287
WHO IS SHE?

40:34.330 --> 40:35.592
TELL ME.

40:35.630 --> 40:36.654
[ Gasping ] I CAN'T.

40:36.700 --> 40:39.089
Cotton:
TELL ME THE NAMES!

40:42.300 --> 40:43.437
Mercy: [ SCREAMS ]

40:43.470 --> 40:45.461
[ PEOPLE SCREAMING ]

40:45.510 --> 40:47.102
[ GROWLING, BARKING ]

40:54.280 --> 40:55.713
Man: MY GOD, MERCY.

40:57.220 --> 40:59.245
Cotton:
THOUGH SHE CANNOT SPEAK A NAME,

40:59.290 --> 41:02.282
SHE WILL SHOW US THE WITCH.

41:07.990 --> 41:09.628
Mercy: [ SCREAMS ]

41:09.660 --> 41:10.649
Woman: OH, NO!

41:10.700 --> 41:11.962
Mercy: [ SCREAMS ]

41:17.000 --> 41:18.865
[ PEOPLE MURMURING ]

41:23.580 --> 41:26.674
[ GROWLING ]

41:36.090 --> 41:37.489
[ SCREAMING ]

41:41.090 --> 41:42.193
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

41:45.670 --> 41:47.092
[ SCREAMS ]

41:50.670 --> 41:51.898
Cotton: [ GRUNTS ]

41:51.940 --> 41:53.908
[ PEOPLE GASP, SCREAM ]

41:53.940 --> 41:56.135
Mercy: [ SCREAMING ]

42:14.060 --> 42:18.019
Isaac: SORRY, CAPTAIN.
YOU CAN'T LEAVE SALEM JUST YET.

42:18.060 --> 42:19.869
SOMETHING YOU'VE GOT TO SEE.

42:30.210 --> 42:33.668
Mary:
IS THIS HIM, THE WITCH?

42:33.710 --> 42:35.519
Cotton: I THINK SO.

42:35.550 --> 42:37.438
ALL THE BOOKS SAY
IF THE VICTIM --

42:37.480 --> 42:39.186
Mary:
NEVER MIND YOUR BOOKS.

42:39.220 --> 42:42.189
IS THIS THE WITCH?

42:42.220 --> 42:44.882
Cotton:
HE WON'T PLEAD EITHER WAY.

42:50.400 --> 42:52.527
Mary: IS THAT SO?

42:52.570 --> 42:57.189
Giles:
WON'T DIGNIFY THE ACCUSATION.

42:57.240 --> 43:03.577
IF YOU CAN CALL A YOUNG GIRL'S
SPIT AN ACCUSATION.

43:04.580 --> 43:11.042
WHAT I HAVE TO SAY,
I'LL SAY TO CAPTAIN JOHN ALDEN.

43:11.080 --> 43:15.050
YOU JUST FIND ME CAPTAIN ALDEN.

43:15.090 --> 43:18.116
I'LL HAVE PLENTY TO SAY.

43:19.990 --> 43:22.424
Cotton: I HAVE SENT MEN
FOR CAPTAIN ALDEN,

43:22.460 --> 43:24.963
BUT I'M TOLD HE'S LEI-T TOWN.

43:28.000 --> 43:30.889
Mary:
JUST OBTAIN A PLEA.

43:30.940 --> 43:33.101
Cotton:
AND IF HE REMAINS SILENT?

43:33.140 --> 43:35.279
Mary:
YOU'VE BEEN GRANTED POWER.

43:35.310 --> 43:37.778
USE IT.
PRESS HIM FOR AN ANSWER.

43:37.810 --> 43:42.611
LET THE SAME DEVIL THAT HOLDS
HIS TONGUE HOLD THE STONES.

43:46.490 --> 43:48.139
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

43:48.190 --> 43:50.511
[ METAL CLANGS ]

43:53.190 --> 43:56.193
Tituba: HURRY.
THE SABBATH IS ABOUT TO BEGIN.

44:22.560 --> 44:26.155
ONE, TWO, THREE, AND FOUR.

44:26.190 --> 44:29.125
RAISE THE DEVIL TO OUR DOOR.

44:29.160 --> 44:32.493
CALL THE PIG, THE WOLF, THE RAM.

44:32.530 --> 44:35.966
COME TO THE CIRCLE,
ALL WHO CAN.

44:36.000 --> 44:39.709
MAKE HIM WALK ON FLOOR TO ROOF.

44:39.740 --> 44:42.868
DRINK TO HIM WITH HORN AND HOOF.

44:42.910 --> 44:45.242
ONE, TWO, THREE, AND FOUR.

44:45.280 --> 44:48.738
THE DEVIL IS HERE.
NOW SLEEP NO MORE.

44:48.780 --> 44:52.511
AND ALL THE WORLD
SHALL BE YOURS IN RETURN.

44:55.390 --> 44:58.518
Mary:
[ INHALES DEEPLY]

44:58.560 --> 45:01.893
[ SIGHS ]

45:04.130 --> 45:06.189
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

45:17.780 --> 45:20.442
John:
IF YOUR WITCHES MEET HERE,

45:20.480 --> 45:22.778
THEY GOT BETTER NIGHT EYES
THAN I DO.

45:22.820 --> 45:24.276
Isaac: [ SCOFFS ]

45:24.320 --> 45:27.118
THEY DON'T NEED NIGHT EYES.

45:27.150 --> 45:29.152
THE NIGHT IS THEIR EYES.

45:31.260 --> 45:34.058
John:
WHAT THE HELL IS THIS?

45:34.090 --> 45:37.719
Isaac:
GIFTS TO THE DEVIL HIMSELF --

45:37.760 --> 45:39.591
THE UNBORN.

46:06.830 --> 46:08.684
[ MOANING ]

46:39.890 --> 46:42.529
Woman:
CRUOUR INNOCENTIA.

46:45.530 --> 46:47.259
WALPU RGISNACHT.

46:47.300 --> 46:49.962
CONSUMMATUM EST.

46:50.000 --> 46:52.468
NOW IT BEGINS.

46:56.910 --> 46:58.844
Isaac: [ SCREAMS ]

47:00.910 --> 47:02.047
Mary: [ SIGHS ]

47:02.080 --> 47:04.878
[ PANTING ]

47:13.360 --> 47:15.794
THE CIRCLE WAS BROKEN.

47:15.830 --> 47:16.990
Tituba: BY WHO?

47:24.740 --> 47:27.629
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

47:27.670 --> 47:28.705
Woman: SATAN!

47:28.740 --> 47:30.002
Cotton: PLEASE, SIR.

47:30.040 --> 47:31.234
I DON'T WANT T0 TO DO THIS.

47:31.280 --> 47:32.907
Giles: THEN DON'T.

47:32.950 --> 47:34.975
Cotton:
BE REASONABLE, MAN.

47:35.020 --> 47:38.239
I HAVE THE POWER
TO PRESS YOU FOR AN ANSWER.

47:38.280 --> 47:43.081
ALL YOU HAVE TO DO IS SAY THE
WORDS "GUILTY" OR "NOT GUILTY,"

47:43.120 --> 47:45.088
AND WE CAN STOP ALL OF THIS.

47:45.130 --> 47:47.928
Giles: IF I SAY "GUILTY,"
YOU'LL HANG ME BEFORE DAWN.

47:47.960 --> 47:49.393
AND IF I SAY NOT,

47:49.430 --> 47:52.729
MY FATE IS STILL IN THE HANDS
OF YOU BASTARDS.

47:52.770 --> 47:55.762
I'LL HOLD MY PEACE
AND TRUST IN THE LORD.

48:03.140 --> 48:05.074
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

48:05.110 --> 48:07.305
Cotton:
LOWER THE STONES!

48:17.760 --> 48:20.456
Giles: [ GROANS ]

48:22.060 --> 48:24.153
Cotton:
I ASK YOU AGAIN.

48:25.630 --> 48:29.134
ARE YOU GUILTY...

48:29.170 --> 48:30.899
OR NOT?

48:30.940 --> 48:32.931
Giles: [ WHIMPERS ]

48:32.970 --> 48:34.631
Isaac: WE'RE DEAD.

48:34.670 --> 48:36.479
John: NO, WE ARE NOT.

48:36.510 --> 48:37.977
Isaac: GOOD AS.

48:38.010 --> 48:39.477
John: I THOUGHT
YOU'VE SEEN THEM BEFORE.

48:39.510 --> 48:41.478
YOU WANTED ME TO SEE THEM,
AND I SAW THEM.

48:41.510 --> 48:42.818
Isaac:
AND THEY SAW US.

48:42.850 --> 48:44.477
AND I TOLD YOU
THEY COULD BE ANYBODY.

48:44.520 --> 48:47.387
John:
OKAY, JUST...CALM DOWN.

48:47.420 --> 48:49.411
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING
IN DISTANCE ]

48:51.990 --> 48:53.480
Giles: [ GROANS ]

48:54.630 --> 48:57.849
Cotton:
HAVE YOU SOMETHING TO SAY?

49:00.770 --> 49:04.035
Giles: MORE STONES.

49:06.470 --> 49:08.938
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

49:11.880 --> 49:13.768
[ GRUNTS ]

49:14.950 --> 49:17.339
John: GILES!
GET THE HELL OFF OF HIM!

49:17.380 --> 49:18.984
[ GRUNTS ]

49:19.020 --> 49:20.817
Giles: ALDEN!

49:22.720 --> 49:24.654
Woman: HE'S DEAD!

49:24.690 --> 49:26.988
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

49:34.700 --> 49:37.999
Cotton:
"WOE TO THE INHABITANTS...

49:38.040 --> 49:41.828
"OF THE EARTH AND OF THE SEA.

49:41.870 --> 49:45.101
FOR THE DEVIL
HAS COME DOWN UNTO YOU."

49:45.150 --> 49:47.038
John: SON OF A BITCH.
SON OF A...

49:50.680 --> 49:52.341
GET!

49:54.350 --> 49:56.181
Cotton: [ MU'I'I'ERING ]

50:01.830 --> 50:07.166
John: MY FATHER'S BOOTS
WERE THE VERY FIRST IN SALEM.

50:08.600 --> 50:11.398
AND I'M WARNING EVERY
GODDAMN ONE OF YOU MURDERING,

50:11.440 --> 50:14.568
HYPOCRITICAL PURITAN BASTARDS

50:14.610 --> 50:17.431
THAT THESE BOOTS
WILL BE THE LAST!

50:39.130 --> 50:41.928
Mary:
I WILL ASK YOU ONCE AGAIN.

50:41.970 --> 50:43.437
WHO WAS THERE?

50:43.470 --> 50:46.109
WHO SAW US?

50:46.140 --> 50:48.267
Mr. Hale:
I WILL TELL YOU AGAIN.

50:48.310 --> 50:50.039
I DO NOT KNOW.

50:51.910 --> 50:54.708
IT IS DIFFICULT TO SEE
PAST A MUZZLE FLASH.

50:54.750 --> 50:59.210
Mary: THEN I SUGGEST
YOU FIND OUT, MR. HALE.

50:59.250 --> 51:01.218
THERE'S NO TURNING BACK.

51:01.250 --> 51:05.459
THE WITCH HUNT HAS BEGUN, AND
WE WILL BE RUNNING THE TRIALS.

51:07.460 --> 51:10.623
YOU UNDERSTAND THAT,
DON'T YOU, GEORGE?

51:10.660 --> 51:13.595
YOU BEST OF ALL.

51:13.630 --> 51:18.693
WE WILL USE THE TRIALS TO TURN
THE PURITANS AGAINST EACH OTHER.

51:18.740 --> 51:23.768
THEY WILL HUNT AND KILL AND
DROWN IN THEIR VERY OWN BLOOD

51:23.810 --> 51:27.644
TILL THERE'S NO PURITANS
LEI-T STANDING...
